These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: weightlifting, biathlon, snowboarding
1. Sport:biathlon is on the right of Sport:snowboarding##1
2. Sport:weightlifting is on the far right##1
3. Sport:weightlifting is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | snowboarding | biathlon | weightlifting |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: avocado, pepper, kiwi
1. Food:pepper is in an odd position##4
2. Food:avocado is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | avocado | kiwi | pepper |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: sudoku, gardening, video-games
1. Hobby:gardening is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:gardening is on the left or right of Hobby:video-games##3
3. Hobby:video-games is on the right of Hobby:gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | sudoku | gardening | video-games |

 #################################
 
